data.description: Don't miss your chance to own this unique Spanish Mediterranean custom home in Circle Mountain Estates!  Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a cozy office space / 4th bedroom, custom light fixtures, island kitchen w/ stainless appliances, spacious living area w/ vaulted beamed ceilings, formal dining, den w/ fireplace and wet bar. This gem of a home has the perk of custom energy efficient sprawling windows throughout. The outdoor space is a true oasis w/ a custom fountain, cabana area w/ pergola, spacious patio and built in grill area, located on .36 acre corner lot!
